    "bio": "Automation specialist helping businesses eliminate manual work using n8n and AI-powered workflows.\nI design custom automations that connect tools like Google Calendar, Airtable, GPT, Supabase, and internal systems turning scattered processes into streamlined operations.\nFrom invoice processing to CRM automation and scheduling systems, I build scalable solutions that save time, reduce errors, and increase efficiency.\nHelping SMBs work smarter without needing a full tech team.",
    "verified": false,
